title: Goals as a Developer
content: To consistently write quality code that follows industry best practices
To make a noticeably positive impact on a team, product, or company
To continuously learn and improve utilizing all available resources

title: My Skillset
content: My ability to learn and problem solve are my greatest skills
JavaScript is my strongest language, with Python in second and C# in third
I can use and understand many frameworks, libraries, and concepts

title: Ideal Work Environment
content: Possesses an overall positive and productive ambience
Has passionate team members who enjoy collaborating
Provides its occupants something to look forward to each day
